                                 <h2 class="title">UK spending axe</h2>
                                 <div class="content">
                                    <ul>
                                       <li class="ts-386x217 first i-w386 i-h217 teaser">
                                          <h3 class="link title"><a href="/web/20101021002905/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/special_reports/spending_review/" class="page">UK Spending Review<img alt="A man holds a mask depicting the face of British chancellor George Osborne"
                                                     width="386"
                                                     height="217"
                                                     src="/web/20101021002905im_/http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/10/20/101020081956_a_man_holds_a_mask_depicting_the_face_of_george_osborne_386x217_nocredit.jpg" /></a></h3>
                                          <p class="summary">The British coalition government has announced the biggest programme of spending cuts in decades, with thousands of public-sector jobs facing the axe. Find out how the Spending Review works and how it will affect you.</p>
